
README (WiDeReDist)

    Project

        WiDeReDist
        Version 1.5.1
        Copyright (C) 2021 by Ralf Kilian

        GitHub: https://github.com/urbanware-org/wideredist
        GitLab: https://gitlab.com/urbanware-org/wideredist

    Definition

        The WiDeReDist project updates Windows Defender definitons (or
        signatures) in internal environments that are completely separated
        from the internet.

        Notice that the project consists of two components.

        This is only the server-side component (for Linux and BSD). The
        client-side component (for Windows) can also be downloaded from the
        GitHub repository.

