    Requirements

        The project does not have many requirements:

            - Some web server such as Apache or nginx (latter has been used in
              development)
            - The 'rsync' package (should already be pre-installed, depending
              on the distribution)
            - The 'wget' package (should already be pre-installed, also
              depending on the distribution)
            - The Bash shell (default in most Linux distributions, but usually
              not on BSD)

    Usage

        You can find the documentation for installation and usage inside the
        official project wiki:

            https://github.com/urbanware-org/wideredist/wiki

